Frequently Asked Questions

Have questions? We've got answers.

Is the free membership, actually free?

Yes — really free. We’ve packed as much value as possible into the free tier so you can start using Ad Alchemy right away. Some advanced features are limited, though, because they rely on expensive AI models and premium APIs. If you need full power, upgrading unlocks everything — but you can get real results without spending a cent.

There's no credit card requirement. There's no free trial auto renewing into a paid membership. I.

Who is Ad Alchemy suited for?

Ad Alchemy is built for anyone running Google Ads. Whether you’re a business owner or new marketer wanting to level up your skills, a seasoned PPC veteran looking to automate and optimise, or an agency trying to scale your processes — Ad Alchemy gives you the tools and insights to run better, smarter campaigns.

Why do you only support Google Ads and Microsoft Ads?

Because we’d rather be the best at one thing than mediocre at everything. Search campaigns are where the highest-intent customers live, so that’s where we focus. No Facebook, no TikTok, no Demand Gen and no Performance Max (for now). Just pure, high-intent search traffic, optimized to deliver maximum ROI.

We do cover some other platforms and campaign types in our Growth Club community though. Other tools like the landing page analysis tool and funnel maps are also super useful if you're looking to optimise your funnel.

What's the Growth Club? And how does it fit with Ad Alchemy?

Ad Alchemy is our toolkit for building better campaigns and optimising your marketing funnel.

The Growth Club is our community where we post advanced tactics, marketing strategy, quick wins and the latest happenings in the digital marketing space. In addition to our work building Ad Alchemy, we still run successful other businesses and we take our learnings and give them directly to members.

Can you build a campaign for me?

Sorry - due to being a small team we can't offer 1 on 1 campaign building. We do post campaign builds in the Growth Club and have a full knowledge base to help you along the way.

Do you have a refund policy?

Best believe! We have a free trial, plus a refund policy. We guarantee that if you apply the TALL strategy and after 60 days you don't make back more than the cost of Ad Alchemy we will refund you.

So what's this SpeedPPC guarantee all about?

It's pretty simple. Consider it a handshake agreement.


If you genuinely try out the TALL Framework and the SpeedPPC platform and after 60 days, you haven't at least covered the costs of SpeedPPC, we'll refund you 100% of your SpeedPPC subscription.


Let us know within 60 days and we'll trigger the refund and cancel your subscription.
